{"tid":1457452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[P牌仔]屌乜姐 走左咪食完飯番黎囉","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:49:58.000Z","uid":274294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7eee625ab975446744e6cb3ef037c5d0fd36bbf9","tid":1457452,"uid":274294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:43:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大量分化post屌手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我知我P牌講野未必有人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先係咁吹風6點清場有大量手足走左<br />\n<br />\n跟手立即極大量分化post屌人散水撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>走左又有乜撚好屌姐</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>返黎咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地係機場坐下佢就就吹大風嚇人走<br />\n<br />\n咪姐係做啱左囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明有手足見到機場復航好失望<br />\n<br />\n但係比D信心其他手足<br />\n<br />\n大家出得去機場一次<br />\n<br />\n就好自然會再翻番黎<br />\n<br />\n而且同一招係唔會對我地有效 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>TWICE</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n記住我地目標唔只係阻佢一兩班機<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而係同港共政府長期抗爭</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁多位手足係一定會翻黎繼續一齊作戰架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以P牌仔係到希望<br />\n<br />\n大家對手足要冷靜D，語氣好D<br />\n<br />\n唔好同自己手足內耗，留番怒氣黎對準政權<br />\n<br />\n我地係因為<span style=\"color: gold;\">不割蓆，不分化</span><br />\n<br />\n先可以同港共對抗到今日<br />\n<br />\n希望留係機場嘅手足唔好咁大力屌走左嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n亦希望走左嘅手足唔好太介懷比人屌，翻番去機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">切記，不割蓆不分化呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">P牌仔第一次出post求輕屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"14c8cf56ac4c40ce22094ee35a9cd30bda1c6dbc","tid":1457452,"uid":274294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:48:06.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0910954573555d94708f536ebc83000c0e73e781","tid":1457452,"uid":274294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:48:22.000Z","msg":"1<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae56866d91c17fced08f5e897cf8432e74bfd0b","tid":1457452,"uid":274294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:48:33.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f68c03dc8fe76f05dfeef6e0a0a4e8e74c6e6ad","tid":1457452,"uid":274294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:48:43.000Z","msg":"3<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f976890a2a6ca56c2b5f6b139cdb004f264f4358","tid":1457452,"uid":274294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:48:53.000Z","msg":"4<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c18205832795ff0a14e9914c1040658d5b71f58","tid":1457452,"uid":274294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:49:04.000Z","msg":"5<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659c3bec506843df1e31ef24debe806eacc5ae1c","tid":1457452,"uid":274294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:49:15.000Z","msg":"6<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86477866737bae6fcccda8c11d438968d377a3e","tid":1457452,"uid":274294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:49:26.000Z","msg":"7<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2cc17120e396012b07d439f1bcba54d447e9d5","tid":1457452,"uid":274294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:49:38.000Z","msg":"8<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786f0d525d02c3fd17e7a9d259c30b42b26dce6b","tid":1457452,"uid":274294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:49:48.000Z","msg":"9<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23fb24a10425f0a9f9c9ec486086d83bfe62c86b","tid":1457452,"uid":274294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:49:58.000Z","msg":"10<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}